  <brief_title>Fingolimod (FTY720) in Acute Demyelinating Optic Neuritis (ADON)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A 48-week, Double-blind, Randomized, Multi-center, Parallel-group Study Comparing Structural Changes in the Retina and Evolution of Visual Function After Immediate Versus Delayed Treatment With Fingolimod in Patients With Acute Demyelinating Optic Neuritis</official_title>
