  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the efficacy and safety of fingolimod 0.5mg versus placebo in patients with
      suspected acute demyelinating optic neuritis (ADON) receiving standard steroid treatment
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
